\c 12
\s Ukubusa kukaJowashi koJuda
\p
\v 1 Ngomnyaka wesikhombisa kaJehu uJehowashi waba yinkosi; wabusa iminyaka engamatshumi amane eJerusalema\x + 2 Lan. 24.1-14.\x*. Lebizo likanina lalinguZibiya weBherishebha\x + Josh. 15.28.\x*.
\v 2 UJehowashi wasesenza okulungileyo emehlweni eN\nd kosi\nd* zonke izinsuku zakhe uJehoyada umpristi amfundisa ngazo.
\v 3 Kodwa indawo eziphakemeyo kazisuswanga; abantu babelokhu benikela imihlatshelo betshisa impepha endaweni eziphakemeyo\x + 14.4. 1 Kho. 15.14.\x*.
\p
\v 4 UJehowashi wasesithi kubapristi: Yonke imali yezinto ezehlukanisiweyo elethwa endlini kaJehova\x + 22.4.\x*, imali yalowo lalowo odlulayo \add kwababaliweyo\add*, imali yalowo lalowo umuntu ayilinganisileyo, yonke imali, okuvela enhliziyweni yaloba nguwuphi umuntu ukuyiletha endlini yeN\nd kosi\nd*\x + Eks. 30.12,16. 2 Lan. 24.6,9.\x*;
\v 5 abapristi kabayithathe kubo, ngulowo lalowo komejwayeleyo, balungise izikhala zendlu\x + Hez. 27.9,27.\x*, loba kungaphi lapho okutholwa khona izikhala\x + 2 Lan. 24.7.\x*.
\v 6 Kodwa kwathi ngomnyaka wamatshumi amabili lantathu wenkosi uJehowashi abapristi babenga\add ka\add*lungisi izikhala zendlu\x + 2 Lan. 24.5,6.\x*.
\v 7 Inkosi uJehowashi yasibiza uJehoyada umpristi labapristi, yathi kibo: Kungani lingalungisi izikhala zendlu? Ngakho-ke lingathathi imali kwelibejwayeleyo kodwa liyinikele izikhala zendlu.
\v 8 Abapristi basebevuma ukuthi kaba\add sa\add*yikuthatha imali ebantwini lokuthi kabayikulungisa izikhala zendlu.
\v 9 UJehoyada umpristi wasethatha ibhokisi elilodwa, wabhoboza isikhala esivalweni salo, walibeka eceleni kwelathi ngakwesokunene nxa umuntu engena endlini yeN\nd kosi\nd*. Abapristi-ke abalinda umbundu bafaka kulo yonke imali eyalethwa endlini yeN\nd kosi\nd*\x + Mark. 12.41. Luka 21.1.\x*.
\v 10 Kwakusithi sebebona ukuthi imali isinengi ebhokisini, umabhalane wenkosi, lompristi omkhulu benyuke\x + 22.4,8. 23.4. 25.18. 2 Lan. 24.11. 26.20. 31.10. Nani 35.25.\x*, bayibophe bayibale imali eyatholwa endlini yeN\nd kosi\nd*\x + 5.23.\x*.
\v 11 Basebenikela imali elinganisiweyo ezandleni zabenzi bomsebenzi, zababonisi bendlu yeN\nd kosi\nd*, bayikhuphela kubabazi bezigodo lakubakhi ababesebenza endlini yeN\nd kosi\nd*\x + 22.5,6.\x*,
\v 12 lakwabakha ngamatshe lakubabazi bamatshe, lokuthenga izigodo lamatshe abaziweyo ukulungisa izikhala zendlu yeN\nd kosi\nd*, lakukho konke okwakhutshelwa indlu ukuyilungisa\x + 22.5,6.\x*.
\v 13 Kodwa kayenzelwanga indlu yeN\nd kosi\nd*\x + 2 Lan. 24.\x* imiganu yesiliva, izindlawu, imiganu yokufafaza, izimpondo zokukhaliswa, \add la\add*ziphi izitsha zegolide lezitsha zesiliva zemali eyalethwa endlini yeN\nd kosi\nd*\x + 25.14,15. 1 Kho. 7.50.\x*,
\v 14 kodwa bayinika abenzi bomsebenzi, basebelungisa ngayo indlu yeN\nd kosi\nd*.
\v 15 Njalo kababalelananga labantu abanikela imali esandleni sabo, ukupha abenzi bomsebenzi, ngoba benza ngokuthembeka\x + 22.7.\x*.
\v 16 Imali yomnikelo wecala\x + Levi 5.15,18.\x* lemali yeminikelo yesono kayilethwanga endlini yeN\nd kosi\nd*\x + Levi 4.24,29.\x*; yayingeyabapristi\x + Levi 7.7. Nani 18.9.\x*.
\p
\v 17 Ngalesosikhathi uHazayeli inkosi yeSiriya\x + 8.12. 1 Kho. 19.17.\x* wenyuka walwa emelene leGathi\x + 1 Sam. 17.4.\x*, wayithumba. UHazayeli wasekhangelisa ubuso bakhe ukwenyuka amelane leJerusalema\x + 8.11. 1 Kho. 2.15.\x*.
\v 18 Kodwa uJehowashi inkosi yakoJuda wathatha zonke izinto ezingcwelisiweyo uJehoshafathi loJoramu loAhaziya oyise, amakhosi akoJuda, ababezingcwelisile\x + 16.8. 18.15,16. 14.14. 1 Kho. 15.18. 1 Kho. 14.26.\x*, lezakhe izinto ezingcwelisiweyo, legolide lonke elatholwa enothweni yendlu kaJehova lendlu yenkosi, wakuthumela kuHazayeli inkosi yeSiriya\x + 12.4.\x*. Wasesenyuka wasuka eJerusalema\x + 2 Lan. 24.23.\x*.
\p
\v 19 Ezinye-ke zezindaba zikaJowashi, lakho konke akwenzayo, kakubhalwanga yini egwalweni lwemilando yamakhosi akoJuda?
\v 20 Inceku zakhe zasezisukuma zenza ugobe, zamtshaya uJowashi endlini yeMilo\x + 14.5. 2 Lan. 24.25-27.\x* eyehlela eSila\x + 1 Lan. 26.16.\x*.
\v 21 Ngoba oJozakari indodana kaShimeyathi loJehozabadi indodana kaShomeri, inceku zakhe, bamtshaya, wafa; basebemngcwaba kuboyise emzini kaDavida. UAmaziya indodana yakhe wasesiba yinkosi esikhundleni sakhe.